[
    {
        "index": 1,
        "start_time": 0,
        "end_time": 7000,
        "text": "Translator: Jessica Ruby\nReviewer: Caroline Cristal"
    },
    {
        "index": 2,
        "start_time": 7161,
        "end_time": 10536,
        "text": "Russia, with the largest territory in the world,"
    },
    {
        "index": 3,
        "start_time": 10536,
        "end_time": 13751,
        "text": "has roughly the same total population as Nigeria,"
    },
    {
        "index": 4,
        "start_time": 13751,
        "end_time": 16255,
        "text": "a country 1\/16 its size."
    },
    {
        "index": 5,
        "start_time": 16255,
        "end_time": 18369,
        "text": "But this similarity won&#39;t last long."
    },
    {
        "index": 6,
        "start_time": 18369,
        "end_time": 21009,
        "text": "One of the populations is rapidly growing,"
    },
    {
        "index": 7,
        "start_time": 21009,
        "end_time": 23427,
        "text": "while the other is slowly declining."
    },
    {
        "index": 8,
        "start_time": 23427,
        "end_time": 25616,
        "text": "What can this tell us about the two countries?"
    },
    {
        "index": 9,
        "start_time": 25616,
        "end_time": 29641,
        "text": "Population statistics are some of the most important data"
    },
    {
        "index": 10,
        "start_time": 29641,
        "end_time": 33367,
        "text": "social scientists and policy experts have to work with."
    },
    {
        "index": 11,
        "start_time": 33367,
        "end_time": 35201,
        "text": "But understanding a country&#39;s situation"
    },
    {
        "index": 12,
        "start_time": 35201,
        "end_time": 37066,
        "text": "and making accurate predictions"
    },
    {
        "index": 13,
        "start_time": 37066,
        "end_time": 40283,
        "text": "requires knowing not just the total size of the population"
    },
    {
        "index": 14,
        "start_time": 40283,
        "end_time": 42403,
        "text": "but its internal characteristics,"
    },
    {
        "index": 15,
        "start_time": 42403,
        "end_time": 45240,
        "text": "such as age and gender distribution."
    },
    {
        "index": 16,
        "start_time": 45240,
        "end_time": 47044,
        "text": "So, how can we keep track of all that data"
    },
    {
        "index": 17,
        "start_time": 47044,
        "end_time": 49867,
        "text": "in a way that makes it easy to comprehend?"
    },
    {
        "index": 18,
        "start_time": 49867,
        "end_time": 51996,
        "text": "Complex data is more easily interpreted"
    },
    {
        "index": 19,
        "start_time": 51996,
        "end_time": 53499,
        "text": "through visualization,"
    },
    {
        "index": 20,
        "start_time": 53499,
        "end_time": 55375,
        "text": "and one of the ways that demographers represent"
    },
    {
        "index": 21,
        "start_time": 55375,
        "end_time": 57919,
        "text": "the internal distribution of a population"
    },
    {
        "index": 22,
        "start_time": 57919,
        "end_time": 60178,
        "text": "is the population pyramid."
    },
    {
        "index": 23,
        "start_time": 60178,
        "end_time": 62451,
        "text": "Here, the data is divided by gender"
    },
    {
        "index": 24,
        "start_time": 62451,
        "end_time": 65510,
        "text": "with females on one side and males on the other."
    },
    {
        "index": 25,
        "start_time": 65510,
        "end_time": 67055,
        "text": "The population numbers are shown"
    },
    {
        "index": 26,
        "start_time": 67055,
        "end_time": 69116,
        "text": "for each five-year age interval,"
    },
    {
        "index": 27,
        "start_time": 69116,
        "end_time": 70974,
        "text": "starting from 0-4"
    },
    {
        "index": 28,
        "start_time": 70974,
        "end_time": 72977,
        "text": "and continuing up to 100 and up."
    },
    {
        "index": 29,
        "start_time": 72977,
        "end_time": 74813,
        "text": "These intervals are grouped together"
    },
    {
        "index": 30,
        "start_time": 74813,
        "end_time": 77570,
        "text": "into pre-reproductive (0-14),"
    },
    {
        "index": 31,
        "start_time": 77570,
        "end_time": 80151,
        "text": "reproductive (15-44),"
    },
    {
        "index": 32,
        "start_time": 80151,
        "end_time": 83369,
        "text": "and post-reproductive years (45 and up)."
    },
    {
        "index": 33,
        "start_time": 83369,
        "end_time": 86126,
        "text": "Such a population pyramid can be a powerful predictor"
    },
    {
        "index": 34,
        "start_time": 86126,
        "end_time": 88117,
        "text": "of future population trends."
    },
    {
        "index": 35,
        "start_time": 88117,
        "end_time": 89576,
        "text": "For example,"
    },
    {
        "index": 36,
        "start_time": 89576,
        "end_time": 93079,
        "text": "Rwanda&#39;s population pyramid shows it to be a fast-growing country,"
    },
    {
        "index": 37,
        "start_time": 93079,
        "end_time": 94670,
        "text": "with most of the population"
    },
    {
        "index": 38,
        "start_time": 94670,
        "end_time": 97450,
        "text": "being in the youngest age groups at the bottom of the pyramid."
    },
    {
        "index": 39,
        "start_time": 97450,
        "end_time": 99704,
        "text": "The number will grow rapidly in the coming years."
    },
    {
        "index": 40,
        "start_time": 99704,
        "end_time": 102537,
        "text": "As today&#39;s children reach their reproductive years"
    },
    {
        "index": 41,
        "start_time": 102537,
        "end_time": 104117,
        "text": "and have children of their own,"
    },
    {
        "index": 42,
        "start_time": 104117,
        "end_time": 107010,
        "text": "the total population is almost certain to double"
    },
    {
        "index": 43,
        "start_time": 107010,
        "end_time": 108617,
        "text": "within the next few decades."
    },
    {
        "index": 44,
        "start_time": 108617,
        "end_time": 110366,
        "text": "For our second example,"
    },
    {
        "index": 45,
        "start_time": 110366,
        "end_time": 111866,
        "text": "let&#39;s look at Canada,"
    },
    {
        "index": 46,
        "start_time": 111866,
        "end_time": 113642,
        "text": "where most of the population is clustered"
    },
    {
        "index": 47,
        "start_time": 113642,
        "end_time": 115394,
        "text": "around the middle of the graph."
    },
    {
        "index": 48,
        "start_time": 115394,
        "end_time": 116811,
        "text": "Because there are less people"
    },
    {
        "index": 49,
        "start_time": 116811,
        "end_time": 118688,
        "text": "in the pre-reproductive age groups"
    },
    {
        "index": 50,
        "start_time": 118688,
        "end_time": 120566,
        "text": "than there are in the reproductive ones,"
    },
    {
        "index": 51,
        "start_time": 120566,
        "end_time": 123238,
        "text": "the population will grow more slowly,"
    },
    {
        "index": 52,
        "start_time": 123238,
        "end_time": 126532,
        "text": "as the number of people reaching their reproductive years decreases."
    },
    {
        "index": 53,
        "start_time": 126532,
        "end_time": 129161,
        "text": "Finally, let&#39;s look at Japan."
    },
    {
        "index": 54,
        "start_time": 129161,
        "end_time": 131158,
        "text": "Because the majority of its population"
    },
    {
        "index": 55,
        "start_time": 131158,
        "end_time": 133162,
        "text": "is in its post-reproductive years"
    },
    {
        "index": 56,
        "start_time": 133162,
        "end_time": 135368,
        "text": "and the number of people is smaller"
    },
    {
        "index": 57,
        "start_time": 135368,
        "end_time": 136873,
        "text": "at each younger interval,"
    },
    {
        "index": 58,
        "start_time": 136873,
        "end_time": 138869,
        "text": "this means that at current rates of reproduction"
    },
    {
        "index": 59,
        "start_time": 138869,
        "end_time": 140782,
        "text": "the population will begin to decline"
    },
    {
        "index": 60,
        "start_time": 140782,
        "end_time": 144590,
        "text": "as fewer and fewer people reach reproductive age."
    },
    {
        "index": 61,
        "start_time": 144590,
        "end_time": 146451,
        "text": "Comparing these three population pyramids"
    },
    {
        "index": 62,
        "start_time": 146451,
        "end_time": 147635,
        "text": "side by side"
    },
    {
        "index": 63,
        "start_time": 147635,
        "end_time": 149220,
        "text": "shows us three different stages"
    },
    {
        "index": 64,
        "start_time": 149220,
        "end_time": 150700,
        "text": "in a demographic transition,"
    },
    {
        "index": 65,
        "start_time": 150700,
        "end_time": 153265,
        "text": "as a country moves from a pre-industrial society"
    },
    {
        "index": 66,
        "start_time": 153265,
        "end_time": 154700,
        "text": "to one with an industrial"
    },
    {
        "index": 67,
        "start_time": 154700,
        "end_time": 156769,
        "text": "or post-industrial economy."
    },
    {
        "index": 68,
        "start_time": 156769,
        "end_time": 158367,
        "text": "Countries that have only recently begun"
    },
    {
        "index": 69,
        "start_time": 158367,
        "end_time": 160147,
        "text": "the process of industrialization"
    },
    {
        "index": 70,
        "start_time": 160147,
        "end_time": 162900,
        "text": "typically see an increase in life expectancy"
    },
    {
        "index": 71,
        "start_time": 162900,
        "end_time": 165074,
        "text": "and a fall in child mortality rates"
    },
    {
        "index": 72,
        "start_time": 165074,
        "end_time": 166654,
        "text": "as a result of improvements"
    },
    {
        "index": 73,
        "start_time": 166654,
        "end_time": 169657,
        "text": "in medicine, sanitation, and food supply."
    },
    {
        "index": 74,
        "start_time": 169657,
        "end_time": 171575,
        "text": "While birth rates remain constant,"
    },
    {
        "index": 75,
        "start_time": 171575,
        "end_time": 173492,
        "text": "leading to a population boom."
    },
    {
        "index": 76,
        "start_time": 173492,
        "end_time": 175370,
        "text": "Developing countries that are farther along"
    },
    {
        "index": 77,
        "start_time": 175370,
        "end_time": 177202,
        "text": "in the industrialization process"
    },
    {
        "index": 78,
        "start_time": 177202,
        "end_time": 179370,
        "text": "begin to see a fall in birth rates,"
    },
    {
        "index": 79,
        "start_time": 179370,
        "end_time": 180669,
        "text": "due to factors such as"
    },
    {
        "index": 80,
        "start_time": 180669,
        "end_time": 184449,
        "text": "increased education and opportunities for women outside of child-rearing"
    },
    {
        "index": 81,
        "start_time": 184449,
        "end_time": 187451,
        "text": "and a move from rural to urban living"
    },
    {
        "index": 82,
        "start_time": 187451,
        "end_time": 189134,
        "text": "that makes having large families"
    },
    {
        "index": 83,
        "start_time": 189134,
        "end_time": 191533,
        "text": "less economically advantageous."
    },
    {
        "index": 84,
        "start_time": 191533,
        "end_time": 194682,
        "text": "Finally, countries in advanced stages of industrialization"
    },
    {
        "index": 85,
        "start_time": 194682,
        "end_time": 195723,
        "text": "reach a point"
    },
    {
        "index": 86,
        "start_time": 195723,
        "end_time": 198451,
        "text": "where both birth and death rates are low,"
    },
    {
        "index": 87,
        "start_time": 198451,
        "end_time": 200229,
        "text": "and the population remains stable"
    },
    {
        "index": 88,
        "start_time": 200229,
        "end_time": 201980,
        "text": "or even begins to decline."
    },
    {
        "index": 89,
        "start_time": 201980,
        "end_time": 204650,
        "text": "Now, let&#39;s take a look at the projected population pyramids"
    },
    {
        "index": 90,
        "start_time": 204650,
        "end_time": 207873,
        "text": "for the same three countries in 2050."
    },
    {
        "index": 91,
        "start_time": 207873,
        "end_time": 209072,
        "text": "What do these tell us"
    },
    {
        "index": 92,
        "start_time": 209072,
        "end_time": 210616,
        "text": "about the expected changes"
    },
    {
        "index": 93,
        "start_time": 210616,
        "end_time": 212371,
        "text": "in each country&#39;s population,"
    },
    {
        "index": 94,
        "start_time": 212371,
        "end_time": 213785,
        "text": "and what kinds of factors"
    },
    {
        "index": 95,
        "start_time": 213785,
        "end_time": 216579,
        "text": "can alter the shape of these future pyramids?"
    },
    {
        "index": 96,
        "start_time": 216579,
        "end_time": 218507,
        "text": "A population pyramid can be useful"
    },
    {
        "index": 97,
        "start_time": 218507,
        "end_time": 220749,
        "text": "not only as a predictor of a country&#39;s future"
    },
    {
        "index": 98,
        "start_time": 220749,
        "end_time": 222951,
        "text": "but as a record of its past."
    },
    {
        "index": 99,
        "start_time": 222951,
        "end_time": 224702,
        "text": "Russia&#39;s population pyramid"
    },
    {
        "index": 100,
        "start_time": 224702,
        "end_time": 227449,
        "text": "still bears the scars of World War II,"
    },
    {
        "index": 101,
        "start_time": 227449,
        "end_time": 230343,
        "text": "which explains both the fewer numbers of elderly men"
    },
    {
        "index": 102,
        "start_time": 230343,
        "end_time": 232093,
        "text": "compared to elderly women"
    },
    {
        "index": 103,
        "start_time": 232093,
        "end_time": 234138,
        "text": "and the relatively sudden population increase"
    },
    {
        "index": 104,
        "start_time": 234138,
        "end_time": 236181,
        "text": "as soldiers returned from the war"
    },
    {
        "index": 105,
        "start_time": 236181,
        "end_time": 238142,
        "text": "and normal life resumed."
    },
    {
        "index": 106,
        "start_time": 238142,
        "end_time": 239783,
        "text": "China&#39;s population pyramid"
    },
    {
        "index": 107,
        "start_time": 239783,
        "end_time": 242784,
        "text": "reflects the establishment of the one child policy"
    },
    {
        "index": 108,
        "start_time": 242784,
        "end_time": 244398,
        "text": "35 years before,"
    },
    {
        "index": 109,
        "start_time": 244398,
        "end_time": 246284,
        "text": "which prevented a population boom"
    },
    {
        "index": 110,
        "start_time": 246284,
        "end_time": 247984,
        "text": "such as that of Rwanda"
    },
    {
        "index": 111,
        "start_time": 247984,
        "end_time": 250073,
        "text": "but also led to sex-selective abortions,"
    },
    {
        "index": 112,
        "start_time": 250073,
        "end_time": 253955,
        "text": "resulting in more male children than female children."
    },
    {
        "index": 113,
        "start_time": 253955,
        "end_time": 256241,
        "text": "Finally, the pyramid for the United States"
    },
    {
        "index": 114,
        "start_time": 256241,
        "end_time": 259435,
        "text": "shows the baby boom that followed World War II."
    },
    {
        "index": 115,
        "start_time": 259435,
        "end_time": 260704,
        "text": "As you can see,"
    },
    {
        "index": 116,
        "start_time": 260704,
        "end_time": 262785,
        "text": "population pyramids tell us far more"
    },
    {
        "index": 117,
        "start_time": 262785,
        "end_time": 263919,
        "text": "about a country"
    },
    {
        "index": 118,
        "start_time": 263919,
        "end_time": 265335,
        "text": "than just a set of numbers,"
    },
    {
        "index": 119,
        "start_time": 265335,
        "end_time": 266951,
        "text": "by showing both where it&#39;s been"
    },
    {
        "index": 120,
        "start_time": 266951,
        "end_time": 268255,
        "text": "and where it&#39;s headed"
    },
    {
        "index": 121,
        "start_time": 268255,
        "end_time": 269673,
        "text": "within a single image."
    },
    {
        "index": 122,
        "start_time": 269673,
        "end_time": 271951,
        "text": "And in today&#39;s increasingly interconnected world,"
    },
    {
        "index": 123,
        "start_time": 271951,
        "end_time": 273970,
        "text": "facing issues such as food shortages,"
    },
    {
        "index": 124,
        "start_time": 273970,
        "end_time": 276972,
        "text": "ecological threats, and economic disparities,"
    },
    {
        "index": 125,
        "start_time": 276972,
        "end_time": 278475,
        "text": "it is increasingly important"
    },
    {
        "index": 126,
        "start_time": 278475,
        "end_time": 280702,
        "text": "for both scientists and policy makers"
    },
    {
        "index": 127,
        "start_time": 280702,
        "end_time": 283145,
        "text": "to have a rich and complex understanding"
    },
    {
        "index": 128,
        "start_time": 283145,
        "end_time": 286903,
        "text": "of populations and the factors affecting them."
    }
]